Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://github.com/tdamiao/cleardocker

Package: cleardocker
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, lsof, deborphan, docker.io
Description: System cleanup script for Debian/Ubuntu
 A complete cleanup script for Debian/Ubuntu systems that cleans APT caches,
 old kernels, systemd logs, temporary files, orphan libraries, and Docker
 resources. It also self-schedules to run weekly via cron.
